</style></head><body style=" font-family:'微软雅黑'; font-size:11pt; font-weight:400; font-style:normal;">
<p style=" margin-top:0px; margin-bottom:0px; margin-left:0px; margin-right:0px; -qt-block-indent:0; text-indent:0px;"><span style=" font-weight:600;">逸便笺_ENote</span><span style=" font-weight:600; text-decoration: underline;">0.2</span> </p>
<p style=" margin-top:0px; margin-bottom:0px; margin-left:0px; margin-right:0px; -qt-block-indent:0; text-indent:0px;"><span style=" font-weight:600; font-style:italic; text-decoration: underline;">使用说明</span>：</p>
<p style=" margin-top:0px; margin-bottom:0px; margin-left:0px; margin-right:0px; -qt-block-indent:0; text-indent:0px;">界面共四个按钮，最左侧的加号按钮可新建一个便笺，而最右侧的按钮可关闭当前便笺而不删除，垃圾桶按钮用于删除当前便笺，&quot;<span style=" font-weight:600;">&gt;</span>&quot;按钮可以查看更多功能。</p>
<p style=" margin-top:0px; margin-bottom:0px; margin-left:0px; margin-right:0px; -qt-block-indent:0; text-indent:0px;">Alt+J 为左对齐 </p>
<p align="center" style=" margin-top:0px; margin-bottom:0px; margin-left:0px; margin-right:0px; -qt-block-indent:0; text-indent:0px;">Alt+E为居中 </p>
<p align="right" style=" margin-top:0px; margin-bottom:0px; margin-left:0px; margin-right:0px; -qt-block-indent:0; text-indent:0px;">Alt+R为右对齐 </p>
<p style=" margin-top:0px; margin-bottom:0px; margin-left:0px; margin-right:0px; -qt-block-indent:0; text-indent:0px;">Ctrl+鼠标滚轮 可暂时缩放所有字体 </p>
<p style=" margin-top:0px; margin-bottom:0px; margin-left:0px; margin-right:0px; -qt-block-indent:0; text-indent:0px;">右键编辑器可以看到设置背景颜色的功能。   </p>
<p style=" margin-top:0px; margin-bottom:0px; margin-left:0px; margin-right:0px; -qt-block-indent:0; text-indent:0px;"><span style=" font-weight:600;">Alt+B </span>为加粗   </p>
<p style=" margin-top:0px; margin-bottom:0px; margin-left:0px; margin-right:0px; -qt-block-indent:0; text-indent:0px;"><span style=" font-style:italic;">Alt+I </span>为斜体   </p>
<p style=" margin-top:0px; margin-bottom:0px; margin-left:0px; margin-right:0px; -qt-block-indent:0; text-indent:0px;"><span style=" text-decoration: underline;">Alt+U</span> 为下划线   </p>
<p style=" margin-top:0px; margin-bottom:0px; margin-left:0px; margin-right:0px; -qt-block-indent:0; text-indent:0px;"><span style=" text-decoration: overline;">Alt+O</span> 为上划线   </p>
<p style=" margin-top:0px; margin-bottom:0px; margin-left:0px; margin-right:0px; -qt-block-indent:0; text-indent:0px;"><span style=" text-decoration: line-through;">Alt+T</span> 为删除线</p>
<p style="-qt-paragraph-type:empty; margin-top:0px; margin-bottom:0px; margin-left:0px; margin-right:0px; -qt-block-indent:0; text-indent:0px;"><br /></p>
<p style=" margin-top:0px; margin-bottom:0px; margin-left:0px; margin-right:0px; -qt-block-indent:0; text-indent:0px;">看到始终存在于右上角的&quot;<span style=" font-weight:600;">X</span>&quot;吗?那是涂鸦功能，可以点击&quot;<span style=" font-weight:600;">&gt;</span>&quot;按钮看到该功能。</p></body></html>